OL,3,CEaster bank holiday expected to be
OL,4,CUK's busiest on roads in four years
OL,6,FDrivers are being warned to expect the
OL,7,Fbusiest Easter on the roads in four
OL,8,Fyears, suggesting many are undeterred
OL,9,Fby rising fuel prices.
OL,11,FThe RAC estimated that nearly 21
OL,12,Fmillion leisure journeys by car are
OL,13,Fplanned between Thursday and Easter
OL,14,FMonday.
OL,16,FIt said that would be the most Easter
OL,17,Ftraffic since 2022, which was the
OL,18,Ffirst bank holiday weekend since
OL,19,FEngland scrapped coronavirus travel
OL,20,Frestrictions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
