FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774872666
OL,3,CEaster bank holiday expected to be
OL,4,CUK's busiest on roads in four years
OL,6,FThe RAC calculated the figure based on
OL,7,Fresponses to a survey of 2,219 UK
OL,8,Fadults conducted between March 20-23,
OL,9,Fwhen fuel prices had already risen
OL,10,Fsignificantly.
OL,12,FOil prices have reached up to 120
OL,13,Fdollars per barrel in response to
OL,14,FIran's stranglehold on tankers passing
OL,15,Fthrough the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,17,FThe AA predicted that traffic during
OL,18,Fthe Easter period will peak on
OL,19,FThursday, when an estimated 21.7
OL,20,Fmillion trips for all journey types
OL,21,Fare planned.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774872666
OL,3,CEaster bank holiday expected to be
OL,4,CUK's busiest on roads in four years
OL,6,FDrivers getting a head start on bank
OL,7,Fholiday getaways will compete for road
OL,8,Fspace with commuters on what is the
OL,9,Flast working day of the week.
OL,11,FThey are advised to set off before
OL,12,F10am if possible to avoid the worst of
OL,13,Fthe congestion.
OL,15,FThe AA forecast that routes to coastal
OL,16,Fdestinations are likely to be
OL,17,Fespecially busy over Easter, alongside
OL,18,Froads around town and city centres,
OL,19,Fplus major retail sites.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
