CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774872666
OL,3,CEaster bank holiday expected to be
OL,4,CUK's busiest on roads in four years
OL,6,FLikely Easter congestion hotspots
OL,7,Fidentified by transport analytics
OL,8,Fcompany Inrix include:
OL,10,FNational Highways has announced it
OL,11,Fwill lift 1,500 miles of roadworks
OL,12,Ffrom its network of motorways and
OL,13,Fmajor A roads in England between
OL,14,FThursday and Easter Monday to ease
OL,15,Fjourneys.
OL,17,FThe RAC said the cost of filling up a
OL,18,Ftypical 55-litre family car with
OL,19,Fdiesel is about #19 higher than on
OL,20,FGood Friday last year, while a tank of
OL,21,Fpetrol is #8 more expensive.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
