OL,3,CEaster bank holiday expected to be
OL,4,CUK's busiest on roads in four years
OL,6,FIt commissioned a survey indicating
OL,7,Fthat 31% of UK drivers are
OL,8,Fincreasingly worried about rising fuel
OL,9,Fcosts.
OL,11,FBut only 6% expect to drive shorter
OL,12,Fdistances because of the issue, and
OL,13,Fanother 6% said they will stop driving.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774872666
OL,3,CEaster bank holiday expected to be
OL,4,CUK's busiest on roads in four years
OL,6,FRAC mobile servicing and repairs team
OL,7,Fleader Sean Kimberlin said: "Despite
OL,8,Ffuel prices rising dramatically due to
OL,9,Fthe conflict in the Middle East, our
OL,10,Fresearch suggests Easter remains
OL,11,Fincredibly important to people as it's
OL,12,Foften the first chance to get away
OL,13,Fsince Christmas or to meet up with
OL,14,Ffriends and family.
OL,16,F"While a significant number of drivers
OL,17,Fare concerned about rising fuel
OL,18,Fprices, a much smaller contingent are
OL,19,Factually changing their plans this
OL,20,FEaster as a result.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774872666
OL,3,CEaster bank holiday expected to be
OL,4,CUK's busiest on roads in four years
OL,6,F"We expect traffic levels to be
OL,7,Fconsistently high from Thursday, when
OL,8,Fmany schools break up."
OL,10,FLee Morley, AA expert patrol, said:
OL,11,F"After what feels like a very long,
OL,12,Fwet winter, lots of families are
OL,13,Flooking forward to the Easter break.
OL,15,F"With more than 20 million journeys
OL,16,Fexpected on the busiest days, it's
OL,17,Fshaping up to be one of the busiest
OL,18,FEasters on the roads in recent years."
OL,26,@pD@WO]sD@AOUzD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
