OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774872666
OL,3,CEaster bank holiday expected to be
OL,4,CUK's busiest on roads in four years
OL,6,FMr Morley urged drivers to carry out
OL,7,Fvehicle checks before setting off,
OL,8,Fsuch as fuel, lights, oil, water and
OL,9,Ftyres.
OL,11,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FThousands of Easter train journeys may
OL,17,Falso be disrupted by Network Rail's
OL,18,Fsix-day shutdown on the West Coast
OL,19,FMain Line (WCML).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
