PN,30410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774872666
OL,3,CEaster bank holiday expected to be
OL,4,CUK's busiest on roads in four years
OL,6,FAvanti West Coast will run services
OL,7,Fbetween Preston and Carlisle via the
OL,8,FSettle and Carlisle line.
OL,10,FBetween Good Friday and Easter Monday,
OL,11,Fservices between London Waterloo and
OL,12,FClapham Junction will be reduced, and
OL,13,Fthere will be no trains between
OL,14,FWinchester and Southampton in
OL,15,FHampshire, or between Herne Bay and
OL,16,FRamsgate in Kent.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
