PN,30411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774872666
OL,3,CEaster bank holiday expected to be
OL,4,CUK's busiest on roads in four years
OL,6,FMeanwhile, EasyJet said it is
OL,7,Fpreparing for its busiest Easter
OL,8,Fgetaway, with up to 16,000 flights
OL,9,Ffrom UK airports during the two-week
OL,10,Fschool break.
OL,12,FIt said the Tenerife and Lanzarote in
OL,13,Fthe Canary Islands and Alicante and
OL,14,FMalaga in mainland Spain are among the
OL,15,Fmost popular destinations.
OL,17,FHoliday company On the Beach said it
OL,18,Fhas seen a surge in last-minute
OL,19,Fbookings for departures this week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
